&amp;=f(p_{k+1}x_{k+1}+\sum_{i=1}^{k} p_{i}x_{i})\\

&amp;=f(\sum_{i=1}^{k+1}p_{i}x_{i})\\

&amp;即 ：\\

\sum_{i=1}^{k+1} p_{i}f(x_i) &amp; \geqslant f(\sum_{i=1}^{k+1}p_{i}x_{i}) ,其中 \sum_{i=1}^{k+1}p_{i}=1\\

